{"tid":1999524,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[求game]想hea玩經營類遊戲 簡單做下決定等成果","createTime":"2020-05-03T08:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T21:03:31.000Z","uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"83b6e25d7c606402a52e76e68e10533ae3c47e15","tid":1999524,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"想揾啲落下order 分配人手 決定方針嘅遊戲<br />\n唔理係city building, 戰爭game, 僱傭兵rpg 定做公司management<br />\n好似city states 咁處理啲policy 但又唔洗好似佢咁逐格起野<br />\n<br />\nManagement元素多啲 分配任務 判斷下需要幾多人手, 資源 就可能派幾個units去執行 亦都可以將啲unit分配職級 可能幾人成小組 幾組成一隊 幾隊成一團/部門<br />\n<br />\n唔想有grinding嘅部分<br />\n<br />\n做下trade, resource management 嘅game都想玩<br />\n如果係city building, 亦都想揾啲採購建材嘅game 揾到咩佢就起咩 睇下個city 發展成點<br />\n<br />\n想揾啲懶懶地 間唔叫番黎有progress嘅game 果啲idle game就得個數字變化唔啱口味<br />\n<br />\n求介紹game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf3d759074025c027821499e2c05699f1111752","tid":1999524,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"動物森友會"},{"pid":"c9269124f008994afee886492e0e4b51766a4b2e","tid":1999524,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"mount and blade？"},{"pid":"24c8fe551d499c0fca92b8ea6c21d6998680bba7","tid":1999524,"uid":282118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"監獄建築師<br />\nRim World"},{"pid":"7cbc0bb8ae281db540aa69faddede5b78219fdf3","tid":1999524,"uid":2974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"Kairosoft系列"},{"pid":"857cdef83623791326d7b8803eadceda97fd27b0","tid":1999524,"uid":277992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"夢幻西餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702b4b4914d1b13d4542b179d8e43e6d5f780930","tid":1999524,"uid":234648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim